[3] Ituri (Beni): recovered patient
Date: Wed 3 Jun 2020
Source: Media Congo [in French, machine trans., abridged, edited]
https://www.mediacongo.net/article-actualite-70072_reapparition_ du_cas_confirme_d_ebola_du_16_avril_2020_evade_ de_son_ isolement_a_beni.html


The confirmed case of the Ebola virus disease of 16 Apr 2020, who had escaped from the health structure of his isolation in Beni, reappeared healthy on Mon 1 Jun in the same city, reports the daily bulletin of the national multisectoral committee of response to Ebola virus disease, reached Tue 2 Jun 2020.

His reappearance comes 45 days after his notification and 49 days after the onset of its symptoms, which dates back to 12 Apr 2020. Investigations are underway to confirm the identity of the patient.

